      • ACCESS_POLICIES

        static final java.lang.String ACCESS_POLICIES
        Property to define authorized access policies. (comma separator)

        Default are: "public", "private", "secret"

        You can override this property to restrict choices.
        You cannot declare new access policies.

        valid uses examples

         jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.access-policies: public
 jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.access-policies: private,secret
        invalid uses examples 
         jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.access-policies: (empty)
 jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.access-policies: custom (unknown access policy)
        Since:
        csp-5.2
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • SIGNUP_POLICIES

        static final java.lang.String SIGNUP_POLICIES
        Property to define authorized signup policies. (comma separator)

        Default are: "free", "request", "admin"

        You can override this property to restrict choices.
        You cannot declare new signup policies.

        valid uses examples 

         jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.signup-policies: free
 jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.signup-policies: request, admin

        invalid uses examples 

         jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.signup-policies: (empty)
 jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.signup-policies: custom (unknown access policy)
 jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.access-policies: secret
 jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.signup-policies: free, request (admin access is missing)
        Since:
        csp-5.2
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
